txt.en: Not all who rise to military prominence are capable of complete conversations. Trolls, known for their strength, sometimes manage small words. For instance, Taskmaster Núrsufum. Apparently, Taskmaster Núrsufum likes to place feathers in his helmet and wants you to go about getting the feathers he desires.
Return to Taskmaster Núrsufum at Tirith Rhaw
Sun-touched eagles are found throughout the Coldfells and sections of Arador's End.\n\nTaskmaster Núrsufum wants you to get him tailfeathers for his helm.
